      "content": "but that's just what people say to make you feel better. the reality is i'm just draining them. i see it in their eyes every single day. and i've been thinking... if i could just go quietly, without making a scene, wouldn't that be a kind thing to do? like, a final way to truly look out for them? to just... stop being an issue?",
